title: Grand Ocean and Bay Views Wonderful Private 1.57 Acre
text:
Grand Ocean and Bay Views Wonderful Private 1.57 Acre ad date: 09/30/2015 
Wonderful Private 1.57 Acre Estate 15929 Pelican Bay Dr., Brookings Pacific Ocean views from spacious living/great room, sunny kitchen, master and bonus room. 2 bedroom, 2 bath home plus office/den in 2,079 sq. ft. Large ocean view deck. Attached 2-car garage with bonus rec room and deck access. Separate RV/boat garage with extra loft area. Newer heat pump, brick fireplace, wood floors and on public water. So many features. A must see!
